WHY ONESTEP?

THE ONESTEP ECOSYSTEM IS SIMPLE AND CONVENIENT. PRIOR EXPERIENCE IN CRYPTO ISN’T REQUIRED. DOWNLOAD THE APP, RENT OR BUY A ONESTEP PAIR, START WALKING, AND GET PAID.

OS ECOSYSTEM

OS APP

Our soon-to-be-released App will be available on the Apple App Store and the Google Play Store. It will make it easy for you to earn money while simply walking.

OS MARKETPLACE

Buy, sell and rent OS sneakers on our integrated marketplace. OS sneakers have different rarities level and some shoes can be worth ten thousands of US dollars.

OS WALLET

It’s time to get your rewards. Swap OS into USDC at any moment with just one click. It was never easier to get rewards for your daily steps.

get rewards every day

Game token: os (onestep)

ONS

Supply and Earning

ONS Tokens may be obtained by physically moving in either Solo Mode or Competition Mode

ONS Burning Mechanics (Destroying)

ONS Tokens are burned by:

  • Shoe Minting
  • Restoring
  • Levelling Up Sneakers
  • Diamond Upgrade
  • Unlocking Scopes

diamonds

Once you reached a specific level, you can unlock Diamonds Scopes and enhance your Sneaker Attributes by embedding them into the Unlocked Scopes (i.e., only the "competition+" Diamonds can enter the "Adaptability" Scope).

There are three different types of Diamonds, each contributes a different Attribute:

blue diamond

(Competition+/Conical Studs NFT)

purple diamond

(Fast+/Rollerblades NFT)

Red diamond

(Comfort+/Ultra-light rubber sole)

ONESTEP IS FAR AHEAD OF ITS TIME

Nothing can compare us in the Move-To-Earn space with extremely innovative features.

OneStep Roadmap

stage 1

Q1: Jan – April 2022

  • A OneStep concept is formed.
  • Layout prototype.
  • Establishing a Team.
  • Creating a narrative and structure for OneStep.

stage 2

Q2: May – July 2022

  • Whitepaper 1.0
  • Solo Mode introduced.
  • GPS/Mobility Sensors and Health data constructed and evaluated for the Anti-Cheatin system.
  • ONS Token launch on the Binance Smart Chain.
  • OneStep NFT layout and marketing.
  • Public pre-sale on PinkSale.

stage 3

Q3: Aug – Oct 2022

  • Diamond and Scopes System debuted.
  • Wallet test phase (OneStep Wallet).
  • Extensive marketing campaign to promote the release of the App's Beta version.
  • “Fusion” and the ability to merge Sneakers in order to generate OG Sneakers (Minting) concept presented.
  • Release of the Beta version of the App on Google Play and Apple Store.

stage 4

Q4: Oct-Dec 2022

  • Competition & Group Modes featured.
  • Laying the finishing touches on the MVP and launching closed beta blockchain testing.
  • OneStep App and website underway.
  • OneStep Application V1 launched on Google Play and Apple Store.
